source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICEHope, is it...? Futile. Utterly futile.
Such feeble light is powerless before darkest despair.
